---
import Layout from "~layouts/index.astro"

import collapseWhitespace from "~utilities/collapseWhitespace"

const ellip = ` … `
const md = " — "

const meta = {
	description: collapseWhitespace(`
		CyberFern helps startups build strong, secure, and resilient
		foundations without breaking the bank. Book a free one-hour
		consultation to understand your real risk picture from day one.
	`),
	title: "Cybersecurity for Startups | CyberFern",
}
---

<Layout {meta}>
	<main id="main-content">
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-text">
				<header>
					<h1>
						You grow your business{ellip}<br />We build your cyber-resilience
					</h1>
				</header>
				<p>Starting up is hard enough without worrying about cybersecurity.</p>
				<p>
					At CyberFern, we guide startups to build strong, secure, and resilient
					foundations without breaking the bank. Our practical, straightforward
					approach helps you to understand and address your security needs, so
					you can focus on <em>growing your business</em>.
				</p>
				<p class="lets-talk">
					<a
						class="button"
						href="https://calendly.com/admin-cyberfern/free-consultation-with-cyberfern"
						rel="external"
						>FREE STARTUP SECURITY CONSULTATION</a
					>
				</p>
				<p>
					<span class="highlight">No pressure, no technical jargon.</span> Just straightforward
					guidance to help your startup grow securely.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-image">
				<picture>
					<source
						srcset="/images/hero.avif"
						type="image/avif"
					/>
					<source
						srcset="/images/hero.webp"
						type="image/webp"
					/>
					<img
						alt=""
						height="450"
						src="/images/hero.jpg"
						width="675"
					/>
				</picture>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="what">
			<header>
				<h2>What We Do</h2>
			</header>
			<div class="card one">
				<picture>
					<source
						srcset="/images/assess-your-cyber-risks.avif"
						type="image/avif"
					/>
					<source
						srcset="/images/assess-your-cyber-risks.webp"
						type="image/webp"
					/>
					<img
						alt=""
						height="300"
						src="/images/assess-your-cyber-risks.jpg"
						width="450"
					/>
				</picture>
				<h3>Assess your cyber risks</h3>
				<p>
					<strong>Know Where You Stand</strong>. We'll review your current setup
					and identify what matters most for your startup's security. Simple,
					practical, and focused on your actual risks.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card two">
				<picture>
					<source
						srcset="/images/build-a-roadmap.avif"
						type="image/avif"
					/>
					<source
						srcset="/images/build-a-roadmap.webp"
						type="image/webp"
					/>
					<img
						alt=""
						height="300"
						src="/images/build-a-roadmap.jpg"
						width="450"
					/>
				</picture>
				<h3>Build a roadmap</h3>
				<p>
					<strong>Clear Steps Forward</strong>. Get a realistic plan that fits
					your budget and growth stage. We prioritise what's crucial now and
					what can wait, so you can make informed decisions about your security
					investments.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card three">
				<picture>
					<source
						srcset="/images/get-help-with-implementation.avif"
						type="image/avif"
					/>
					<source
						srcset="/images/get-help-with-implementation.webp"
						type="image/webp"
					/>
					<img
						alt=""
						height="300"
						src="/images/get-help-with-implementation.jpg"
						width="450"
					/>
				</picture>
				<h3>Get help with implementation</h3>
				<p>
					<strong>Hands-On Support</strong>. Need help putting the plan into
					action? We're here to guide you through each step, from setting up
					basic protections to training your team. No stress{md}just steady
					progress toward better security.
				</p>
			</div>
			<p class="lets-talk">
				<a
					class="button"
					href="https://calendly.com/admin-cyberfern/free-consultation-with-cyberfern"
					rel="external"
					>BOOK YOUR FREE CONSULTATION</a
				>
			</p>
		</section>
		<section class="expect">
			<header>
				<h2>What to Expect</h2>
			</header>
			<div>
				<p>
					Your free one-hour consultation is a no-strings conversation about
					where your startup stands today and what you actually need. Anna has
					run startups herself, so she understands the pressure to move fast and
					the temptation to leave security for later.
				</p>
				<p>
					In that hour, you'll get a clear picture of your biggest risks, a
					sense of what's urgent and what can wait, and honest advice on next
					steps{md}whether that involves CyberFern or not.
				</p>
				<p class="lets-talk">
					<a
						class="button"
						href="https://calendly.com/admin-cyberfern/free-consultation-with-cyberfern"
						rel="external"
						>BOOK YOUR FREE CONSULTATION</a
					>
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
